snippet.title: Fat Bear Week - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Fat Bear Week is a third person, single player action paced collectathon full of delicious food to eat and secrets to find.

Become the fattest bear before winter comes!
Available on Itch.io: https://teamfatbears.itch.io/fatbearweek
